
                         SprngBoot + Angular – CRUD

For start:

1)	Generating a table in a database (PostgreSQL) in the directory: 
          ./sql
2)	The parameters of access to the database are set in the directory: 
          ./server in file: application.yml 
3)	Server start:
          AppMain.java
4)	Running angular in terminal: ./ui (on any port): 
          ng serve --open 

____________________________________________________________________________________

Following technologies stack are used in the project 'SprngBoot + Angular – CRUD':
_____________________________________________________________________________________

  • SpringBoot 2.3.5.RELEASE (Spring Data JPA / Web / Test )

  • Spring Aspects 5.2.10

  • Hibernate-core 5.4.22

  • PostgreSQL 42.2.18

  • Javax.validation-api  2.0.1

  • lombok 1.8.18

  • modelmapper 2.3.9

  • apache-commons-lang 3.3.10

  • Angular 11.1.4 ( Material )

  • JDK 1.11

  • Junit5
